text: In this task, you will hear a sequence of words with different pitches, a pause, then a singular word. Your task is to determine whether the PITCH of this singular word was in the previous sequence. After hearing the singular word, you will be prompted to indicate whether the pitch of the word was "absent" or "present" from the sequence. Press "Next" to start trials.
